data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 1/27 11-2PM Don’t miss out on this beautiful home on the west side of Pensacola in the sought after Tarkiln Ridge Estates neighborhood. GREAT LOCATION! Close to Beaches, NAS Military Base, State Parks, shopping and schools. 3-Bedroom and 2-bathroom 2 car garage. Kitchen has nice classic white cabinets and quartz countertops.  Kitchen includes a breakfast nook area. Bathrooms have updated cabinets with Corian countertops (both have double vanities), beautifully done.  Large Master bedroom has trey ceiling and walk in closet.  Master bath has a double vanity, garden tub and separate shower.  Flooring is the same throughout home; luxury vinyl planks; tiled bathrooms and laundry room area.  Second and third bedrooms are spacious with good-sized closets.  High ceilings in living room area which includes a cozy fireplace, great for entertaining guests.  Gas stove top and oven.  Refrigerator, washer and dryer do convey.  Roof replaced in 2020.  Screened in Back patio.  Come make this home your “Home Sweet Home” today.
